      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0636P0-03054'>
        <a name='S5LV0636P0_20020619_GCR_21'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-robin-bridgeman' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0636P0_20020619_GCR_21' title='Link to this speech by Mr Robin Bridgeman' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
